title: Live the dream life in our gorgeous community! Stop by for a tour!
posting_body: ['Come home to a great community - Park San Dimas Senior Apartments!', 'Address:', '265 W Foothill Blvd', 'San Dimas, CA 91773', 'Beds:', '2  /', 'Baths:', '1 /', 'Size:', '750 sq ft', 'Monthly Rent:', '$2455', 'Senior Community!', 'Experience resort style living at an award-winning community.', 'Enjoy the scenic mountain views, immerse yourself in our sparkling pool, unwind in our hot tub or exercise in our 24-Hour State of the Art Fitness Center.', 'Gaze at the moonlight stars in our park-like setting community with lush landscaping.', 'We invite you to explore our private clubhouse with complimentary wi-fi.', 'Spend time with neighbors and friends in our social lounge enjoying the many planned activities.', 'Schedule a Tour:', '<URL>', 'Security Deposit:', '$650', 'Length of Lease:', 'Variable', 'show contact info', 'Property Features:', '● BBQ Area', '● Carport', '● Courtyard', '● Covered Parking', '● Free Weights', '● Gameroom', '● Library', '● Media Room', '● Package Receiving', '● Short Term Lease', '● 24 Hour State of the Art Fitness Center', '● Community Hosted Events', '● Entertainment Clubhouse', '● Laundry Facilities', '● Near Dining and Shopping', '● On-Site Maintenance', '● On-Site Management', '● Public Transportation', '● Resort Style Living', '● Spanish Speaking Staff', 'Apartment Amenities:', '● Air Conditioning', '● Cable Ready', '● Disposal', '● Gas Range', '● Huge Pantries', '● Large Closets', '● Spacious Kitchens', '● Storage Units', '● Upgraded Flooring', '● Window Coverings', 'Pets:', 'Max 2 allowed, Max weight 35 lb each, Rent $50.00, Deposit $400.00.', 'Breed restrictions apply.', 'Business Hours:', 'Mon - Fri: 10:00 AM - 4:00 PM', 'Sat: 10:00 AM - 4:00 PM', 'Ready to Lease?', 'Call our office at', 'show contact info', 'Website:', '<URL>', 'Proudly managed by REMM Group', 'THE REMM GROUP (DRE LICENSE #01949006)', 'EQUAL HOUSING OPPORTUNITY', '1C1AB7B380DD425']
